File: compiler/js-native-context-specialization.cc
Symbol: JSNativeContextSpecialization::Reduce (handles various JS ops)
Snippet: effect = BuildCheckEqualsName(name, key, effect, control);
Note: JSNativeContextSpecialization references simplified()->ReferenceEqual(), NumberEqual(), and builds checks; possible folding of JSEqual against null/undefined occurs via BuildJumpIfEqual etc; protector dependency registration might be elsewhere (compilation-dependencies).
explanation: Entry pointing to JSNativeContextSpecialization usage sites that may fold equality to reference checks against null/undefined and rely on protector state indirectly.
